title: Malone's weight throw highlights Tigers' outing at Texas Tech - Auburn Tigers Official Athletic Site
content: Malone's weight throw highlights Tigers' outing at Texas Tech  Auburn Tigers Official Athletic Site
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – Senior thrower Madi Malone delivered the biggest performance for the Auburn track and field team over the weekend at Texas Tech's Open and Multis as the All-American won first place in the women's weight throw with a season's-best mark of 22.31m/73-2.50.
